songs.title: Exalted
songs.lyrics:
[Producer Tag]
Foliage

[Verse 1]
Embers of a love thought lost burns
Deep inside hollow husk
Remind yourself it's always there
Reasons unknown I care for
All you've lost all you'll find
In this beautiful life
You are living here
Take my hand, nothing to fear
You walk your own path
No one's fault, just you to blame
You're not to blame
We are the same

[Chorus]
Embers of love thought lost
Embers of love thought lost
Kinder the fire, this moss
Winter is here, I'm gone

[Verse 2]
What if it was all my fault?
Take your pain, take it off
Your flesh my bone
My weakness God knows that
I wanna live so long
My rapture is to come
Keep me here
Please my dear
My dear...

[Producer Tag]
Foliage
